---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Documentation">
	<main class="py-20 px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Hero Section -->
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                    Welcome to the Laravel Mail documentation
                </h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Laravel Mail is an open source marketing automation platform built with Laravel framework that provides you with the greatest level of audience intelligence, thus enabling you to make more meaningful customer connections.
                </p>
			</div>

			<!-- Quick Links -->
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
				<a href="/docs/api" class="group">
					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-payflo-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-payflo-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 group-hover:text-payflo-blue transition-colors duration-200">API Reference</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-600">Detailed docs of our REST API endpoints and parameters.</p>
					</div>
				</a>

				<a href="/docs/index" class="group">
					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-payflo-purple/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-payflo-purple" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 group-hover:text-payflo-purple transition-colors duration-200">Tutorials</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-600">Step-by-step guides to help you get started with our platform.</p>
					</div>
				</a>


			</div>

			<!-- Getting Started Section -->
			<div class="mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Getting Started</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Quick Start Guide</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Get up and running with Leads Captain in minutes.</p>
						<ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-4 text-gray-600">
							<li>Sign up for an account</li>
							<li>Configure your email settings</li>
							<li>Add your first subscriber</li>
						</ol>
						<a href="/docs/index" class="mt-6 inline-block text-payflo-blue hover:text-payflo-purple font-medium">
							Read the guide →
						</a>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Integration Guide</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Learn how to integrate <b>Laravel Mail</b> with your existing systems.</p>
						<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-4 text-gray-600">
							<li>API authentication</li>
							<li>Webhooks setup</li>
							<li>Data synchronization</li>
							<li>Error handling</li>
						</ul>
						<a href="/docs/index" class="mt-6 inline-block text-payflo-blue hover:text-payflo-purple font-medium">
							View integration docs →
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>


			<div class="mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Popular Topics</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
					<a href="/docs/campaigns" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2" title="laravel mail campaigns">Campaigns</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600">
                            If you’re trying to connect with your audience, an email campaign is the way to go. Think of it as a bundle of emails — whether it’s for a new product launch or your monthly newsletter.
                        </p>
					</a>

					<a href="/docs/configuration" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Configuration</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600">
							Complete reference documentation for setting up and configuring email marketing campaigns in the Laravel Mail platform.
						</p>
					</a>


					<a href="/docs/email-services" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Email Services</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600">Generate and customize marketing platform reports.</p>
					</a>


                    <a href="/docs/subscribers" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Subscribers</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Generate and customize marketing platform reports.</p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="/docs/tags" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Tags</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Generate and customize marketing platform reports.</p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="/docs/template" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Templates</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Generate and customize marketing platform reports.</p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="/docs/workflows" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Workflows</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Generate and customize Workflows marketing automation.</p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="/docs/workspaces" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Workspaces</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Crate and manage marketing platform workspaces.</p>
                    </a>


					<a href="/docs/messages" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Messages</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600">Learn about our security features and best practices.</p>
					</a>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
